      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IT'S SNOWTIME (1) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Below best last time at this track (24.30) in a Grade 6, finishing a 8 length sixth. Rates on top and should go close. CANYA DIG DEEP (7) slotted in just off the lead from the wide box before lifting strongly to score (23.92) at this track in a Maiden over 407m. Won at her only start from this draw. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. DARK END (6) is rarely out of the finish, recording eight places from 15 starts. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when third (24.08) at this track. Hard to beat again. IT'S ME HI (2) put a gap on her rivals last start. That form reads well.",
